{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.1","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:1","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.002.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Joram, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl. Guerre contre les Moabites<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-27: cf. 2 R 1:17. 2 Ch 18:1-8. Ps 107:4-6, 35.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Joram, fils d\u2019Achab, r\u00e9gna sur Isra\u00ebl \u00e0 Samarie, la dix-huiti\u00e8me ann\u00e9e de Josaphat, roi de Juda. Il r\u00e9gna douze ans.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.2","name":"2 Rois 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.2.25","name":"2 Rois 2:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.2.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.2","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:2","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, non pas toutefois comme son p\u00e8re et sa m\u00e8re. Il renversa les statues de Baal que son p\u00e8re avait faites;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.3","name":"2 Rois 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.1","name":"2 Rois 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.3","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:3","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>mais il se livra aux p\u00e9ch\u00e9s de J\u00e9roboam, fils de Nebath, qui avait fait p\u00e9cher Isra\u00ebl, et il ne s\u2019en d\u00e9tourna point.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.4","name":"2 Rois 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.2","name":"2 Rois 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.4","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:4","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>M\u00e9scha, roi de Moab, poss\u00e9dait des troupeaux, et il payait au roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl un tribut de cent mille agneaux et de cent mille b\u00e9liers avec leur laine.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.5","name":"2 Rois 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.3","name":"2 Rois 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.5","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:5","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>A la mort d\u2019Achab, le roi de Moab se r\u00e9volta contre le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.6","name":"2 Rois 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.4","name":"2 Rois 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.6","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:6","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Le roi Joram sortit alors de Samarie, et passa en revue tout Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.7","name":"2 Rois 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.5","name":"2 Rois 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.7","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:7","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Il se mit en marche, et il fit dire \u00e0 Josaphat, roi de Juda: Le roi de Moab s\u2019est r\u00e9volt\u00e9 contre moi; veux-tu venir avec moi attaquer Moab? Josaphat r\u00e9pondit: J\u2019irai, moi comme toi, mon peuple comme ton peuple, mes chevaux comme tes chevaux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.8","name":"2 Rois 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.6","name":"2 Rois 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.8","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:8","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et il dit: Par quel chemin monterons-nous? Joram dit: Par le chemin du d\u00e9sert d\u2019\u00c9dom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.9","name":"2 Rois 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.7","name":"2 Rois 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.9","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:9","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, le roi de Juda et le roi d\u2019\u00c9dom, partirent; et apr\u00e8s une marche de sept jours, ils manqu\u00e8rent d\u2019eau pour l\u2019arm\u00e9e et pour les b\u00eates qui la suivaient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.10","name":"2 Rois 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.8","name":"2 Rois 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.10","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:10","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Alors le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl dit: H\u00e9las! L\u2019\u00c9ternel a appel\u00e9 ces trois rois pour les livrer entre les mains de Moab.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.11","name":"2 Rois 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.9","name":"2 Rois 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.11","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:11","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Mais Josaphat dit: N\u2019y a-t-il ici aucun proph\u00e8te de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, par qui nous puissions consulter l\u2019\u00c9ternel? L\u2019un des serviteurs du roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl r\u00e9pondit: Il y a ici \u00c9lis\u00e9e, fils de Schaphath, qui versait l\u2019eau sur les mains d\u2019\u00c9lie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.12","name":"2 Rois 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.10","name":"2 Rois 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.12","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:12","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Et Josaphat dit: La parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel est avec lui. Le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, Josaphat et le roi d\u2019\u00c9dom, descendirent aupr\u00e8s de lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.13","name":"2 Rois 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.11","name":"2 Rois 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.13","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:13","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>\u00c9lis\u00e9e dit au roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: Qu\u2019y a-t-il entre moi et toi? Va vers les proph\u00e8tes de ton p\u00e8re et vers les proph\u00e8tes de ta m\u00e8re. Et le roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl lui dit: Non! Car l\u2019\u00c9ternel a appel\u00e9 ces trois rois pour les livrer entre les mains de Moab.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.14","name":"2 Rois 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.12","name":"2 Rois 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.14","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:14","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>\u00c9lis\u00e9e dit: L\u2019\u00c9ternel des arm\u00e9es, dont je suis le serviteur, est vivant! Si je n\u2019avais \u00e9gard \u00e0 Josaphat, roi de Juda, je ne ferais aucune attention \u00e0 toi et je ne te regarderais pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.15","name":"2 Rois 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.13","name":"2 Rois 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.15","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:15","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Maintenant, amenez-moi un joueur de harpe. Et comme le joueur de harpe jouait, la main de l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut sur \u00c9lis\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.16","name":"2 Rois 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.14","name":"2 Rois 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.16","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:16","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Et il dit: Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Faites dans cette vall\u00e9e des fosses, des fosses!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.17","name":"2 Rois 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.15","name":"2 Rois 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.17","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:17","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Car ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Vous n\u2019apercevrez point de vent et vous ne verrez point de pluie, et cette vall\u00e9e se remplira d\u2019eau, et vous boirez, vous, vos troupeaux et votre b\u00e9tail.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.18","name":"2 Rois 3:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.16","name":"2 Rois 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.18","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:18","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Mais cela est peu de chose aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Il livrera Moab entre vos mains;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.19","name":"2 Rois 3:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.17","name":"2 Rois 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.19","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:19","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>vous frapperez toutes les villes fortes et toutes les villes d\u2019\u00e9lite, vous abattrez tous les bons arbres, vous boucherez toutes les sources d\u2019eau, et vous ruinerez avec des pierres tous les meilleurs champs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.20","name":"2 Rois 3:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.18","name":"2 Rois 3:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.20","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:20","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Or le matin, au moment de la pr\u00e9sentation de l\u2019offrande, voici, l\u2019eau arriva du chemin d\u2019\u00c9dom, et le pays fut rempli d\u2019eau.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.21","name":"2 Rois 3:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.19","name":"2 Rois 3:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.21","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:21","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Cependant, tous les Moabites ayant appris que les rois montaient pour les attaquer, on convoqua tous ceux en \u00e2ge de porter les armes et m\u00eame au-dessus, et ils se tinrent sur la fronti\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.22","name":"2 Rois 3:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.20","name":"2 Rois 3:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.22","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:22","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Ils se lev\u00e8rent de bon matin, et quand le soleil brilla sur les eaux, les Moabites virent en face d\u2019eux les eaux rouges comme du sang.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.23","name":"2 Rois 3:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.21","name":"2 Rois 3:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.23","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:23","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Ils dirent: C\u2019est du sang! Les rois ont tir\u00e9 l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e entre eux, ils se sont frapp\u00e9s les uns les autres; maintenant, Moabites, au pillage!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.24","name":"2 Rois 3:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.22","name":"2 Rois 3:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.24","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:24","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Et ils march\u00e8rent contre le camp d\u2019Isra\u00ebl. Mais Isra\u00ebl se leva, et frappa Moab, qui prit la fuite devant eux. Ils p\u00e9n\u00e9tr\u00e8rent dans le pays, et frapp\u00e8rent Moab.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.25","name":"2 Rois 3:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.23","name":"2 Rois 3:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.25","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:25","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Ils renvers\u00e8rent les villes, ils jet\u00e8rent chacun des pierres dans tous les meilleurs champs et les en remplirent, ils bouch\u00e8rent toutes les sources d\u2019eau, et ils abattirent tous les bons arbres; et les frondeurs envelopp\u00e8rent et battirent Kir-Har\u00e9seth, dont on ne laissa que les pierres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.26","name":"2 Rois 3:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.24","name":"2 Rois 3:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.26","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:26","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Le roi de Moab, voyant qu\u2019il avait le dessous dans le combat, prit avec lui sept cents hommes tirant l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e pour se frayer un passage jusqu\u2019au roi d\u2019\u00c9dom; mais ils ne purent pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.27","name":"2 Rois 3:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.25","name":"2 Rois 3:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.27","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 3:27","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.3.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Il prit alors son fils premier-n\u00e9, qui devait r\u00e9gner \u00e0 sa place, et il l\u2019offrit en holocauste sur la muraille. Et une grande indignation s\u2019empara d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, qui s\u2019\u00e9loigna du roi de Moab et retourna dans son pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3","name":"2 Rois 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.1","name":"2 Rois 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.26","name":"2 Rois 3:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb4566290.17977295');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb4566290.17977295\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb4566290.17977295","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb4566290.17977295'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb4566290.17977295\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}